To begin:
  Create empty database
  Enter database information in 'database.yaml'
  Run 'command/migrate' once to set up database
  Write 'workstations.rb' to set up workstations
  Write 'schedule.yaml' and run 'command/schedule' to prepare schedule

To use:
  Run 'command/start' to start factory
  Run 'command/stop' to stop factory

To modify:
  Change 'workstations.rb' and run 'command/update' to update factory while running*
  Change 'schedule.yaml' and run 'command/schedule' to update schedule while running*
  
  *updates take effect when current workstation finishes its run
